r />\n<br />\n//筆者親身訪問了十位90後俄羅斯朋友，半數表示會投票，認為投票是盡公民責任。當中會投票的大多支持普京，認同他的外交政策及認為他為俄國帶來穩定。至於<span style=\"color: red;\">一位反普京的朋友表示，投白票抗議並不可行，因白票最終會被非法手段轉化成支持普京的選票，故她會投票給其他候選人。</span>綜合而言，俄羅斯年輕人雖然並不熱衷於投票，但樂於表達自己的看法。而從言談間感受到90後俄羅斯人對未來更加悲觀，厭倦普京長時期執政。//</blockquote><br />\n俄國含撚派"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"佢覺得普京(低得票率)+其他候選人(高得票率) = 成功<br />\n<br />\n投白票唔work係因為會俾人做手腳 <br />\n仲話無論普京/其他候選人都會俾錢買票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06f713b73634d7d262b4fe197a5cf3a47ba48a5","tid":596934,"uid":92964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:44:31.000Z","msg":"驚咩吖，普京又搬梅德韋傑夫出嚟，自己做第二，6年後又一條好漢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d730b57ed3060c62bd458b29daaaaa5b17e219c","tid":596934,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef07e728e4e04fdee21208b77f1568068484e961","tid":596934,"uid":3864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac8de7f89bc9d28721a6d2b6638252608876e30a","tid":596934,"uid":61091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作者：佛蘭克 （莫斯科國立國際關係學院碩士生；研究中俄關係和歐亞政治）<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E5%8F%8A%E5%BE%8C%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%2F&d=Ji9LS5VDi9nEuzr0mj97mdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1d61dfeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%2599%2582%25